tool_input.script:
export const meta = {
  name: 'qa-semantic-search',
  description: 'Execute semantic search for QA workflow',
  phases: [
    { title: 'SemanticSearch', detail: 'Search knowledge files for relevant sections' }
  ]
}

phase('SemanticSearch')

const result = await agent(`
You are executing the semantic-search workflow for nabledge-6 knowledge base.

## Task
Search the knowledge base for sections relevant to the following query:
"テスト時だけシステム日時を任意の日付に差し替える方法はあるか？本番とテストで切り替えたい（目的: 仕組み・動作を理解したい）"

## Knowledge base location
/home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6/knowledge/

## Semantic Search Workflow
Execute the workflow defined in:
/home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6/workflows/semantic-search.md

The query is: "テスト時だけシステム日時を任意の日付に差し替える方法はあるか？本番とテストで切り替えたい（目的: 仕組み・動作を理解したい）"

processing_type is null (cross-functional)
purpose is 仕組み・動作を理解したい

## Instructions
1. Read the semantic-search.md workflow file
2. List all JSON files in the knowledge directory
3. For each page, evaluate relevance to the query about replacing system date/time during testing
4. Select relevant pages and sections
5. For each page record why it was selected or skipped
6. For each section record why it was selected (high/partial) or skipped

## Output format (JSON)
{
  "selected_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<one sentence>"}
  ],
  "excluded_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<one sentence>"}
  ],
  "selected_sections": [
    {"file": "<full file path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "relevance": "<high|partial>", "reason": "<one sentence>"}
  ],
  "excluded_sections": [
    {"file": "<full file path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "reason": "<one sentence>"}
  ]
}
`, {
  label: 'semantic-search',
  phase: 'SemanticSearch',
  schema: {
    type: 'object',
    properties: {
      selected_pages: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            path: { type: 'string' },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['path', 'reason']
        }
      },
      excluded_pages: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            path: { type: 'string' },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['path', 'reason']
        }
      },
      selected_sections: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            file: { type: 'string' },
            section_id: { type: 'string' },
            relevance: { type: 'string', enum: ['high', 'partial'] },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['file', 'section_id', 'relevance', 'reason']
        }
      },
      excluded_sections: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            file: { type: 'string' },
            section_id: { type: 'string' },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['file', 'section_id', 'reason']
        }
      }
    },
    required: ['selected_pages', 'excluded_pages', 'selected_sections', 'excluded_sections']
  }
})

return result
